The project, called “Bud Light N3XT Collection” will be available to consumers 21 and over. The NFTs are part of a larger launch of the company’s first zero-carb beer. <br data-v-f87c67ca="">
<br data-v-f87c67ca="">
With the purchase of an NFT, consumers will have the opportunity to vote on Bud Light NEXT merchandise, have access to Bud Light NEXT brand and partner events, and more.&nbsp;
